{"tid":1866392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你個14日強制隔離原來只係「打電話問疫情」","createTime":"2020-02-06T17:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T02:53:42.000Z","uid":5416,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9b42681b180c92394dee79e67734b9239a142440","tid":1866392,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dbc.131/photos/a.122771689139239/166460624770345\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdbc.131%2Fphotos%2Fa.122771689139239%2F166460624770345&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=06131707\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dbc.131/photos/a.122771689139239/166460624770345</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgZfM5g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgZfM5g.jpg&h=08ae26d5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n【強制檢疫靠「義工」 大玩「打電話問病情」咁兒戲？】<br />\n<br />\n本台收到港大及中大高年級醫科生的消息，指於晚上（6）收到校方通知，政府14天隔離令實施在即，預料檢疫相關的工作量將會大增。衛生署希望本地醫學院五年級及六年級同學義務協助衛生署進行相關檢疫工作。工作主要為：<br />\n<br />\n1. 打電話監察正接受強制檢疫人士，以確保他們遵守隔離令；<br />\n2. 協助進行醫學隔離；及<br />\n3. 在有需要時，提供健康相關建議。<br />\n<br />\n文/C<br />\n圖/J<br />\n<br />\n#DBC #加山傳播 #香港人加油 #特區政府 #我只想 #身體健康 #武漢肺炎 #洗手洗手洗手 #醫科生 #義工<br />\n<br />\n屌你如果條友cut線咁你撚知佢係咪屋企<br />\n封關唔封 大家等冚家鏟未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d5a7f2e53dce3d605b3f7435e2f14d80736ef1","tid":1866392,"uid":319616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"黑警比人影到係警車交收CSI口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1866377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1866377</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e8761354a0d69dc2ac8d324c0112c985cb3ca9c5","tid":1866392,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:19:47.000Z","msg":"全民肺炎"},{"pid":"731d92929c51fcf3dc00853752d347f84f213c27","tid":1866392,"uid":90987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep